            <p class="eyebrow">Service overview</p>
            <h2>What catch basin cleaning actually solves</h2>
            <p>A catch basin is engineered with a sump that traps grit and debris before water enters the outlet pipe. When the sump fills, the basin stops trapping anything and debris flows into the outlet line.</p><p>Honest Drain vacuums the sump, removes accumulated grit and trash, jets the outlet line if needed, and documents the basin condition for the property file.</p>
            <p class="link-row"><a class="text-link" href="../../../contact.html">Book a service visit</a></p>
